snippet.title: college decision reactions 2020 (20+ ivies harvard, yale, princeton, mit, penn, columbia, dartmouth)
snippet.description:
hi:) this is my first youtube video ever!!!! 
here I react to ~20 college decisions (7 Ivies) for the Class of 2024 with lots of unwarranted and rambling commentary. 

pls like so i’ll have the motivation to make more  lmfao
& comment down questions/ideas (i’ll try to get to as many as possible)
& follow my IG @laurenliuuu

hey guys! thank u for all the support:) 
- a few of you are asking me for my gpa/sat and I made another video for all of that good stuff, revealing my stats: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-aOH_0_RskQ 
- I realize a lot of you have questions about the college application process. I’d recommend y’all check https://joinbullseye.com/lauren-liu for a FREE Strategy Session for college application advice and essay editing tips from professionals (who actually know what they’re doing lol). Go to https://joinbullseye.com/lauren-liu  to get a free Ivy League Strategy Session with Ivy League College Advisors from Harvard, Standard, UPenn, Princeton, Brown and UCLA. best of luck xx 

college i applied to: Harvard, University of Pennsylvania (UPenn), Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT), Dartmouth, Princeton, Columbia, University of Chicago (UChicago), Yale, UC Berkeley (Cal), UCLA, Wellesley, Cornell, Amherst, Northeastern (NEU), Yale NUS, Rutgers + more I think

(yingying's ig is @yingg.zhao and she's yale 2024 bound)
